                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6779" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0146</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7863 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金孔雀飞来 基诺山寨笑 ——创新突围助力旅游扶贫和乡村振兴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Golden Peacock is Flying, Jinuo Shangzhai Village Laughs——Innovation Breakthrough Helps Tourism Poverty Alleviation and Rural Revitalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵书虹，孔营营，杨兰，张鸿，李琴，倪向丽（通讯作者）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南金孔雀旅游集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南金孔雀旅游集团；基诺山寨；投资与决策；旅游；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yunnan Golden Peacock Tourism Group; Jinuo Shangzhai village; investment and decision-making; tourism;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金孔雀旅游集团在2005年接管负债累累的基诺山寨，积极探索推进“政府+企业+村寨”的旅游扶贫开发模式，通过科学运营和不断创新，带领基诺山寨实现了跨越发展，获得了良好的经济效益、社会效益与环境效益。进入新的发展阶段，基诺山寨的经营和发展也涌现出新的问题亟待解决……本案例以金孔雀旅游集团为例，介绍企业如何在偏远的民族地区带领村寨通过旅游实现脱贫，同时探讨兼顾政府旅游扶贫、社区利益和公司经营效益三方共赢模式的建构与发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2005, Golden Peacock Tourism Group took over the heavily indebted Jinuo Shanzhai Village, actively explored and promoted the tourism poverty alleviation and development mode of &quot;government+enterprises+villages&quot;, and through scientific operation and continuous innovation and development, led Jinuo Shanzhai Village to achieve leapfrog development, and achieved good economic, social and environmental benefits. However, in a new stage of development, new problems have emerged in the operation and development of Jinuo Shanzhai ... This case takes Golden Peacock Tourism Group as an example to introduce how enterprises can lead people to poverty alleviation through tourism in remote ethnic areas, and at the same time, discuss the construction and development of a three-way win-win model that considers government tourism poverty alleviation, community interests and company operating benefits.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任、双赢理论；利益相关者理论、利益共同体；社会责任创新、企业经营创新；三重底线理论、可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-11</td>
                            </tr>
